metadata.description:
Is that all?

No debrief? No "enjoy the rest of your life"? Not even the fucking bell?

No lifejacket, just some vague acknowledgement that I already know how to swim, so of course I'll be fine.

Adrift doesn't even begin to describe it...

And as for those new troubles...?

"What troubles?"
